{"tid":1799852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方批評示威者破壞食店要求交出閉路電視可悲 屬「黑社會手法」","createTime":"2019-12-27T09:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T13:07:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":247,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"60f579dcc9a5e4041a0ef64a1bb4fc1e7f7a49fb","tid":1799852,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓說，示威者的仇恨及暴力破壞聖誕節，針對商場大肆破壞，又騷擾市民，投擲花盆及漆彈，破壞食肆，令商店無法做生意，批評有人要求食店交閉路電視被拒後，就破壞食店，食店之後要交出閉路電視，令人感到可悲，形容屬黑社會手法。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，示威者在油尖旺街頭破壞，包括打爛玻璃、焚燒銀行、港鐵站及電箱，向警車投擲汽油彈，批評他們目無法紀，擔心暴力行為恆常化，大眾會麻木，令社會變得更危險。<br />\n<br />\n郭嘉銓又說，警方有責任維持治安，聖誕節前後進入商場執法，目的是保護市民，呼籲市民及受害商戶報案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499815-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499815-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=f4d6c561\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499815-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=87cb5ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499815-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78e408aaf04887288b27b36ff33e055726533b0","tid":1799852,"uid":997,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"跟你地學野咋"},{"pid":"f0be4bc2c8780b0fbc2d055dde5a624c4ec12d2d","tid":1799852,"uid":88133,"like":156,"dislike":2,"score":154,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"黑社會話人地黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84a5e53962add9ae4057aa4e302c9775b80be7f","tid":1799852,"uid":161726,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"noted<br />\n乜野叫黑社會手法?<br />\n唔聽人講就打?<br />\n警察都係咁喎。"},{"pid":"01da5e51fff8cae0d61958f6219520